    <div class="container">
        <div class="card is-clickable">
            <header class="card-header" onclick="toggleElement('faq_05', true)">
                <p class="card-header-title title my-4">What if a competition does not sell out?</p>
                <button class="card-header-icon" aria-label="more options">
                    <span id="iconfaq_05" class="icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-angle-down" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                    </span>
                </button>
            </header>
            <div id="faq_05" class="card-content" style="display: none;">
                <div class="content">
                    If a traditional or automated draw that you have entered does not sell out, the draw will still take place and you will have a better chance of winning than if it had sold out! Each draw is guaranteed to take place on the date and time shown on the entry page. All sold tickets are still valid and we will generate a random number until we have a winner. If there are instant win prizes which have not been won within the time limit of the competition, they will be forfeited, however each ticket purchased into the competition will still be included in the end prize draw, if applicable.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
