            <div id="faq_08" class="card-content" style="display: none;">
                <div class="content">
                    Instant win competitions have predetermined prizes with numbers allocated to them at the time the competition launches. If you buy a ticket into a competition with instant wins and one or more of your ticket numbers match the list of predetermined numbers, you will win the prize(s) allocated to it. Some instant win competitions have an ‘end prize’ where every entry purchased into the instant win competition will be entered to win the end prize, drawn as a traditional or automated draw at the end of the competition.  
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
